  • Constructor Details

    • TrajectorySelector

      public TrajectorySelector(Path directory)
      Class to automatically load and display Trajectory information. This class will automatically scan a selected dir (shallow scan) and attempt to load every file. The loaded trajectories will be displayed in a sendable chooser on smartdashboard. Field2ds can also be added so that displayed trajectories automatically update with changes.
      Parameters:
      directory - Directory to load Trajectory json files from

      public void linkField(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.smartdashboard.Field2d field)
